<plot>On the night of December 24th, two children sneak out of their bedroom in the hope of seeing 'Santa Claus' when he visits them. When he appears in their living room, they ask him what he does during the rest of the year. So Santa proceeds to tell them all about the Land of Winter, where he lives, the creatures that live there, and how he and his helpers make toys for children all over the world.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?477071</url></doc>
